    function arctan(uint256 x) public view returns (uint256) {
        if (x < 2) {
            return 0;
        }

        uint8 bit = log_2(x);
        uint256 base = 1 << bit;
        uint256 db = data[bit];
        uint256 db0 = data[bit - 1];
        return ((db - db0) * (x - base)) / base + db0;
    }

    function log_2(uint256 x) internal pure returns (uint8) {
        uint8 res = 0;

        if (x < 256) {
            while (x > 1) {
                x >>= 1;
                res += 1;
            }
        } else {
            for (uint8 s = 128; s > 0; s >>= 1) {
                if (x >= (1 << s)) {
                    x >>= s;
                    res |= s;
                }
            }
        }

        return res;
    }
